score(String) - Method in class com.example.qrapp.ScanActivity
SHA-256 hashed barcode is passed into this function and uses a scoring method to determine the arbitrary worth of the barcode based on subsequent repeated numbers/letters - where the score grows exponentially according to the length of the combo chain.
